          "value": "# Aurora One — Technical Specifications\n\nThe Aurora One is a lightweight urban electric bike. It ships with a 500 Wh removable battery and a 250 W mid-drive motor. The assisted top speed is 25 km/h and the rated range is up to 80 km per charge in eco mode. The complete bike weighs 17 kg and fits riders from 160 cm to 195 cm tall. Frame material is 6061 aluminium; wheel size is 27.5 inches.",
