        "parent_id": null,
        "type": "nodetool.input.StringInput",
        "data": {
          "name": "doc_charging",
          "value": "# Aurora One — Battery & Charging\n\nThe Aurora One battery charges from empty to full in about 4 hours with the included standard charger, or reaches 80% in roughly 2 hours. An optional fast charger cuts a full charge to about 2.5 hours. The battery is removable, so it can be charged on or off the bike. Aurora recommends storing the battery between 20% and 80% charge when not riding for long periods.",
          "description": "Document 2 of your knowledge base"
